WEBVTT

00:13.028 --> 00:14.764
[ Helicopter blades whirring ]

00:17.967 --> 00:19.903
[ Sirens wailing ]

00:23.975 --> 00:25.644
Okay, listen up.

00:25.744 --> 00:28.848
I want every call, no matter
how trivial, charted on the map.

00:28.948 --> 00:31.517
You get a hot shot, a cluster,
you send a car.

00:31.617 --> 00:33.286
I don't care if somebody calls,

00:33.386 --> 00:35.356
says they saw a guy
with a band-aid on his nose,

00:35.456 --> 00:38.826
black eye -- get the location,
put it on the map.

00:38.926 --> 00:41.663
Okay. Head on a swivel.

00:41.763 --> 00:43.197
Let's find this asshole.

00:43.298 --> 00:46.235
[ Telephones ringing,
indistinct conversations ]

00:47.270 --> 00:48.705
Anything, kiz?

00:48.805 --> 00:50.740
Not a lot of working cameras
over there.

00:50.840 --> 00:52.476
Bangers see to that.

00:52.576 --> 00:54.412
Jerry, what do you got
on the abandoned factory?

00:54.512 --> 00:56.381
I went back
on the title search 40 years.

00:56.481 --> 00:57.715
Started as cold storage,

00:57.815 --> 00:59.117
then a brake-pad factory,
home insulation.

00:59.217 --> 01:00.852
Insulation.

01:00.952 --> 01:03.188
Waits said
his father worked in that area,

01:03.289 --> 01:04.391
got sick from asbestos
or something.

01:04.491 --> 01:05.658
That's how
he knew the place.

01:05.758 --> 01:07.394
Kiz, we're gonna need
the Van video.

01:07.494 --> 01:09.062
Take a look what waits said
on the ride over.

01:09.162 --> 01:10.097
On it.

01:10.197 --> 01:11.665
Hey.

01:11.765 --> 01:13.200
Phones ringing off the hook.
That's a good sign.

01:13.301 --> 01:15.637
Yeah, lots of sightings.
Nothing solid yet.

01:15.737 --> 01:18.773
We think he abandoned a jacked
pickup in Lincoln heights.

01:18.873 --> 01:21.210
Owner was found in the back
under a tarp, shot in the face.

01:21.311 --> 01:23.346
[ Sighs ]
Jesus, Mary, and Joseph.

01:23.446 --> 01:25.782
So we're searching
the alleys in the area,

01:25.882 --> 01:27.318
going house to house.

01:27.351 --> 01:29.052
My guess is he probably stole
another vehicle

01:29.153 --> 01:30.555
in that neighborhood.

01:30.655 --> 01:31.889
What do you want me
to do, Harry?

01:31.989 --> 01:33.325
[ Sighs ]

01:33.425 --> 01:35.561
Waits got crate's badge
and gun.

01:35.661 --> 01:37.430
Fuck me.

01:37.530 --> 01:39.666
All right, we got to put out
an all-units broadcast.

01:39.766 --> 01:42.502
Can you write something up,
get it out to communications?

01:42.602 --> 01:45.072
Yeah. Oh, man.
Pounds is gonna shit blood.

01:45.172 --> 01:46.541
Forget pounds, all right?

01:46.641 --> 01:48.776
Let's grab up this asshole,
get crate's stuff back.

01:48.876 --> 01:49.945
Yeah, right.

01:52.348 --> 01:54.350
[ Insects chirping ]

02:40.872 --> 02:42.941
*

