32:15.730 --> 32:17.665
But I need my glasses.

32:17.765 --> 32:20.401
Yeah, well, you can listen to
your programs till I get back.

32:20.536 --> 32:23.772
[ Door opens, closes ]

32:23.872 --> 32:25.842
Bosch:
Pack of b's, please.

32:25.942 --> 32:27.610
[ Cash register beeps, dings ]

32:35.887 --> 32:37.556
Shit.

32:59.281 --> 33:00.750
[ Engine shuts off ]

33:03.820 --> 33:06.190
[ Dog barking in distance ]

33:17.503 --> 33:19.138
[ Thudding ]

33:19.238 --> 33:21.008
[ Safety clicks ]

33:40.330 --> 33:42.299
L.A.P.D.
Let me see your hands!

33:42.399 --> 33:43.635
[ Gasping ]

33:43.668 --> 33:45.938
Jesus Christ, Sheila.
[ Safety clicks ]

33:46.038 --> 33:47.640
What the hell
are you doing here?

33:47.740 --> 33:49.808
I -- I came
to get the cat.

33:49.908 --> 33:52.679
I-i was just
looking around.

33:52.779 --> 33:54.714
You scared the hell out of me.
[ Chuckles ]

33:54.814 --> 33:57.351
You can't be in here.
It's an ongoing investigation.

33:57.451 --> 33:59.186
I didn't know.

33:59.286 --> 34:00.354
I-I'm sorry.

34:00.454 --> 34:01.723
What about buddy?

34:01.823 --> 34:03.291
You can take him.

34:06.062 --> 34:07.664
[ Cat meows ]

34:25.718 --> 34:27.888
[ Engine turns over ]

36:07.808 --> 36:11.277
[ Sniffs, sighs ]

36:11.377 --> 36:14.048
[ Cellphone buzzing ]

36:18.921 --> 36:22.190
[ Buzzing continues ]

37:21.261 --> 37:22.729
Hey.

37:22.897 --> 37:24.799
You need a lift?

37:24.900 --> 37:26.534
I might.

37:26.634 --> 37:28.170
Hop in.

37:28.270 --> 37:30.106
Cool.

37:34.311 --> 37:35.913
Oh, you're cute.

37:35.946 --> 37:38.449
Thanks.

37:38.549 --> 37:40.518
You too.

37:40.618 --> 37:43.322
Pull around the corner.

37:45.157 --> 37:47.326
Or I could
just do you here?

37:47.426 --> 37:51.697
I was...Thinking maybe something
a little more relaxing.

37:51.797 --> 37:55.069
Really?

37:55.169 --> 37:56.370
Yeah.

37:56.470 --> 37:57.604
Spend the night.

38:00.943 --> 38:02.777
I'm game.

38:02.945 --> 38:05.181
[ Engine turns over ]
Me too.

38:05.281 --> 38:07.250
Buckle up.

38:17.795 --> 38:20.166
Woman:
Plus, the citywide manhunt

38:20.266 --> 38:24.704
for escaped confessed serial
killer raynard waits continues.

38:24.804 --> 38:26.506
All that
and weather coming up.

38:26.606 --> 38:27.807
[ TV shuts off ]

38:27.975 --> 38:31.279
Hey, mind, uh,
putting that back on?

38:31.379 --> 38:33.747
I was hoping to catch
the weekend weather.

38:33.848 --> 38:35.317
Sure.

38:35.417 --> 38:37.352
[ TV turns on ]
...How to ask a lady on a date.

38:37.452 --> 38:38.587
Thanks.

38:38.687 --> 38:40.256
Coming up, the 911 call

38:40.356 --> 38:43.293
that landed this don Juan
in jail.

38:43.393 --> 38:46.497
What do you say we get
this party started, huh?

38:46.597 --> 38:48.065
Mm.

38:48.165 --> 38:50.202
...southern California
of a serious scam.

38:50.302 --> 38:53.105
Foreigners are calling people,
posing as IRS officers.

38:53.205 --> 38:54.807
Take it
nice and slow.

38:54.907 --> 38:58.011
They tell their victims they
owe money to the government.

38:58.077 --> 39:01.315
Want it slow?

39:01.415 --> 39:03.117
Come here.

39:03.217 --> 39:04.519
...has received 50 reports...

39:04.619 --> 39:06.754
What's down here?
...In just the last few days.

39:06.854 --> 39:11.060
Ohh.
One of them lost $17,000
when she bought...

39:11.160 --> 39:13.762
Why don't we let him come out
and play, huh?

39:13.862 --> 39:16.066
Slow.

39:16.166 --> 39:18.435
Oh, is that you want,
daddy?

39:18.535 --> 39:20.204
Oh.

39:20.304 --> 39:23.841
Investigators say they can't
do very much about it...

39:23.941 --> 39:26.511
Oh. [ Chuckles ]

39:26.611 --> 39:28.613
Man:
The ongoing police manhunt...
There you go, huh?

39:28.713 --> 39:30.816
...for escaped serial killer
raynard waits...

39:30.916 --> 39:32.618
About time.
...Turned hectic today

39:32.718 --> 39:35.056
when a police vehicle collided
with a bus and a parked car

39:35.122 --> 39:37.224
on a busy street in Hollywood.
I was beginning to think
you were shy.

39:37.324 --> 39:39.393
Slow.
The officer driving
that vehicle

39:39.493 --> 39:42.430
was responding to one of dozens
of tips police received today

39:42.530 --> 39:46.402
in response to
the $150,000 reward...
[ Whimpers, gasps ]

39:46.502 --> 39:48.804
...the l.A.P.D. Has offered
for information leading

39:48.904 --> 39:50.507
to the arrest of the fugitive.

39:50.607 --> 39:53.810
Waits was arrested last week
on suspicion of murder

39:53.910 --> 39:56.747
when police discovered
a dead body in his work Van.

39:56.847 --> 39:58.149
[ Bone cracks ]

39:58.249 --> 39:59.785
He subsequently confessed
to murdering

39:59.885 --> 40:01.953
as many as seven young men
in the Hollywood area.

40:02.088 --> 40:03.289
[ Sighs, panting ]

40:03.389 --> 40:05.225
Waits also
claimed responsibility

40:05.325 --> 40:07.927
for the death of the boy
whose bones recently were found

40:08.027 --> 40:10.064
on a hillside in Laurel canyon.

40:10.164 --> 40:11.832
Two days ago,
while leading investigators

40:11.932 --> 40:15.036
to the remains of his alleged
victims, waits escaped,

40:15.137 --> 40:17.572
killing deputy
district attorney Luis Escobar

40:17.672 --> 40:21.577
and seriously wounding
an l.A.P.D. Detective.

40:21.677 --> 40:23.146
If you have seen waits

40:23.246 --> 40:24.647
or have information
on his whereabouts,

40:24.747 --> 40:32.056
call the l.A.P.D. Tip line
at 323-555-0172.
